    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>首先从adobe网站上下载linux版本的tar.gz压缩包。解压到Home下的个人目录。打开终端运行如下命令</p><p>1、Firefox<br>安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir ~/.mozilla/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">cp ~/libflashplayer.so ~/.mozilla/plugins</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>移除并还原到稳定版本<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rm ~/.mozilla/plugins/libflashplayer.so</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>2、Chrome (需要root权限)<br>备份及安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mv /opt/google/chrome/libgcflashplayer.so /opt/google/chrome/libgcflashplayer.so-backup</span><br><span class="line">sudo cp ~/libflashplayer.so /opt/google/chrome/libgcflashplayer.so</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>移除并还原到稳定版本<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo mv /opt/google/chrome/libgcflashplayer.so-backup /opt/google/chrome/libgcflashplayer.so</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>另外，64位系统用户可以通过这个PPA来安装，支持Ubuntu 10.04 ~ 11.10 (source: wowubuntu.com)<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:sevenmachines/flash</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install flashplugin64-installer</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
