    <title>archlinux安装记录</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/wiki/archlinux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/wiki/archlinux安装记录/</id>
    <published>2019-01-28T06:40:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-28T09:13:02.012Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>基础系统安装</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dhcpcd</span><br><span class="line">passwd root</span><br><span class="line">rc.d start sshd</span><br><span class="line">cfdisk</span><br><span class="line">mkfs.ext2 /dev/sda1</span><br><span class="line">mkswap /dev/sda2 &amp;&amp; swapon /dev/sda2</span><br><span class="line">mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3</span><br><span class="line">mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda4</span><br><span class="line">mount /dev/sda3 /mnt</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /mnt/boot &amp;&amp; mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/boot</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /mnt/boot/efi &amp;&amp; mount /dev/sda0 /mny/boot</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /mnt/home &amp;&amp; mount /dev/sda4 /mnt/home</span><br><span class="line">nano /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span><br><span class="line">Server = http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch</span><br><span class="line">Server = http://mirrors.163.com/archlinux/$repo/os/$arch</span><br><span class="line">pacstrap /mnt base base-devel</span><br><span class="line">pacstrap /mnt grub-bios</span><br><span class="line">genfstab -p /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab</span><br><span class="line">arch-chroot /mnt</span><br><span class="line">nano /etc/hostname</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime</span><br><span class="line">nano /etc/locale.gen</span><br><span class="line">locale-gen</span><br><span class="line">echo LANG=zh_CN.UTF-8 &gt; /etc/locale.conf</span><br><span class="line">pacman -S efibootmgr</span><br><span class="line">grub-install /dev/sda</span><br><span class="line">grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg</span><br><span class="line">pacman -S net-tools</span><br><span class="line">pacman -S vim</span><br><span class="line">passwd</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br><span class="line">umount /mnt</span><br><span class="line">umount /mnt/boot/</span><br><span class="line">umount /mnt/home/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>图形界面安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano /etc/pacman.conf  </span><br><span class="line">加入 </span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxfr]</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Never</span><br><span class="line">Server = http://repo.archlinux.fr/$arch</span><br><span class="line">加入</span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Optional TrustedOnly</span><br><span class="line">Server = http://repo.archlinuxcn.org/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>安装钥匙<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yaourt -S archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reboot</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -Syy</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -Sf filesystem</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -Su</span><br><span class="line">useradd 用户名</span><br><span class="line">passwd 用户名</span><br><span class="line">usermod -G wheel,network,video,audio,optical,storage,power,dbus,hal 用户名</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /home/用户名</span><br><span class="line">chmod 777 /home/用户名</span><br><span class="line">chown 用户名 /home/用户名</span><br><span class="line">reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装基础显示<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yaourt -S xorg-server xorg-xinit xorg-utils xorg-server-utils mesa-demos xorg-twm xorg-xclock xterm mesa</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /etc/X11/xinit/xinitrc ~/.xinitrc</span><br><span class="line">安装显卡驱动：yaourt -S xf86-video-nv</span><br><span class="line">安装触摸板驱动：yaourt -S synaptic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:openbox+xfce4</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S lxde gnome kde...</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S wqy-microhei;lxappearance</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S clearlooks-colors-gtk-theme安装gtk的clearlooks系列</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">:cinnamon</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S cinnamon</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S slim</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable slim</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S fcitx fcitx-configtool</span><br><span class="line">:fcitx输入法设置</span><br><span class="line">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export XMODIFIERS=&quot;@im=fcitx&quot;</span><br><span class="line">:安装网络管理</span><br><span class="line">yaourt -S networkmanager</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable networkmanager.service</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">挂载光盘</span><br><span class="line">mount -t auto -o ro /dev/cdrom /mnt/cdrom</span><br><span class="line">挂载ISO文件</span><br><span class="line">mount -t iso9660 -o loop /*.iso /mnt/cdrom</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">aur</span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">#The Chinese Arch Linux communities packages.</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Optional TrustAll</span><br><span class="line">Server   = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/$arch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">#The Chinese Arch Linux communities packages.</span><br><span class="line">SigLevel = Optional TrustedOnly</span><br><span class="line">Server   = http://repo.archlinuxcn.org/$arch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[archlinuxfr]</span><br><span class="line"> Server = http://repo-fr.archlinuxcn.org/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​    </p><p><strong> 硬盘安装方法</strong></p><ol><li>提取vmlinuz、archiso.img、iso包</li><li><p>改grub4dos的menu.lst加入</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title Install Arch Linux</span><br><span class="line">root (hd0,0)</span><br><span class="line">kernel /vmlinuz archisolabel=archiso</span><br><span class="line">initrd /archiso.img</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启引导</p></li><li>挂载/ISO<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># mkdir /iso</span><br><span class="line"># mount -r -t ntfs /dev/sda1 /iso</span><br><span class="line"># modprobe loop</span><br><span class="line"># losetup /dev/loop6 /iso/archlinux-2012.10.06-dual.iso</span><br><span class="line"># ln -s /dev/loop6 /dev/disk/by-label/archiso</span><br><span class="line"># exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
    
